snippet: Apple and Google, along with other technology companies, made it into the top 10 of Interbrand’s annual report.
abstract: Apple and Google head annual Interbrand Best Global Brands report for third year in row; report estimates that Apple brand is worth $170.3 billion, while Google brand is worth $120.3 billion.
lead_paragraph: Apple and Google, along with other technology companies, made it into the top 10 of Interbrand’s annual report.

headline.main: Tech Giants Top Best Global Brands List
headline.print_headline: Apple and Google Take Top Spots on Best Global Brands List for 2nd Straight Year
